                "category": "defensive",
                "deathNote": true,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>If the unrisen Slithermaw is reduced to 0 Hit Points by means other than fire damage, disintegration, damage caused by a character wearing Slithermaw's Bane, or his resurrection vulnerability, he returns to unlife at the start of his next turn. He has 150 Hit Points and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone] in the space in which he was destroyed. He can't be returned to unlife by this ability again for 1 hour.</p>"
