                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The unrisen reshapes its grotesque form to move swiftly. It Strides twice. Any living creature that can see the unrisen during this movement must succeed at a @Check[fortitude|dc:37] save or be @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2} on a critical failure). This is a mental and visual effect. The unrisen can't use Awful Approach again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Awful Approach]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
